== About me 
I am an Assistant Professor in the [https://aem.eng.ua.edu/ Department of Aerospace Engineering and Mechanics] at the University of Alabama, leading the [https://sites.google.com/view/ascl-ua Controls and Autonomy Lab (CAL)]. Before joining UA in August 2023, I was a Postdoctoral Researcher in the Department of Mechanical Science and Engineering at the University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. \n\n

My research interests include *control theory*,  autonomous systems, aerial robotics, and applications to aerospace and agriculture. In particular, we develop and test control and decision-making algorithms to ensure the safem, robust, and efficient operation of autonomous systems in dynamic and uncertain environments. 


