== News #{{<font color=red><b>}} Opening {{</b></font>}} 
- 03/2026: I am delighted and grateful to receive the [https://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/show-award?AWD_ID=2542222 NSF CAREER Award]! My sincere thanks to the DCSD program for their support!
- 07/2025: I served on an NSF Panel.
- 06/25/2025: I co-organized and gave a talk for the [https://ecc25.csiefoundation.am/ workshop on Safe Control and Learning in Autonomous Systems at ECC 2025]. 
- 10/2024: I organized and gave a talk for the [https://mecc2024.a2c2.org/tutorial-sessions/ tutorial session on Safety-Critical Control Under Uncertainties at MECC 2024]. 
- 06/2024: I served on two NSF panels. 
- 04/2024: I gave a talk at the [https://mwcgt2024.northwestern.edu/ 2024 Midwest Workshop on Control and Game Theory]. 
- 02/2024: I served on an NSF panel. 
- 01/2024: I gave a talk for the University of New Mexico ME department. 

